   "version": 1,
   "type": "sm_game",
   "content": [
      {
         "id": "bb055408-8647-4346-b300-1e993d782f5a",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">In this phase, we will explore:</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">In science, after formulating a hypothesis, it is essential to test it rigorously.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Simple answers to complex problems can often be misleading.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">The choice of words used to formulate a hypothesis can significantly impact its strength.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "e4f52862-3969-4551-a015-0313b61669fc",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "e4f52862-3969-4551-a015-0313b61669fc",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Introduction</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">When documents or chronicles containing names are absent, research can come to a halt.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">An alternative approach is to consider estimating connections based on available evidence.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "006119b3-0a8a-492c-ab43-35cc20ad08c9",
         "prev": "bb055408-8647-4346-b300-1e993d782f5a",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "006119b3-0a8a-492c-ab43-35cc20ad08c9",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">In this stage of the game, your goal is to answer the following question:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflection 1: On Grandparents</b><br />Did the firstborn receive a name from one of the grandfathers?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "4c2e805a-a364-48c7-939c-b4dbfb5174e5",
         "prev": "e4f52862-3969-4551-a015-0313b61669fc",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "4c2e805a-a364-48c7-939c-b4dbfb5174e5",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">We need to define the hypotheses, which means we are establishing the possible answers to be tested:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HYPOTHESIS 1</b>: All firstborns receive a name from one of their grandfathers.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HYPOTHESIS 2</b>: This happens sometimes, but it cannot be considered a general rule.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HYPOTHESIS 3</b>: This never happens.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "09b4c8c7-be35-428a-ad4c-f4aee65aa354",
         "prev": "006119b3-0a8a-492c-ab43-35cc20ad08c9",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "09b4c8c7-be35-428a-ad4c-f4aee65aa354",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Validating <b>HYPOTHESIS 1</b></span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">To verify this hypothesis, we will examine several inventories from S\u00e3o Paulo, Brazil. We begin with the inventory of Lucr\u00e9cia Leme, wife of Fern\u00e3o Dias Paes:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgLL\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgLL', '0%')\" class=\"imgcenter\" src=\"images/Archive/LucreciaLeme.png\" style=\"width: 30%;\" /><b>Figure 1</b>: Excerpt from the inventory of Lucr\u00e9cia Leme (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('3a98a6a5-5261-4d8a-b10b-05f7ff97b790'); return false;\">Invent\u00e1rios e Testamentos, <span class=\"htdate\"></span>, Volume 14, pp. 314</a>)</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "963f42db-7221-42ca-8584-7d1412773c0a",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 0,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "top"
      },
      {
         "id": "963f42db-7221-42ca-8584-7d1412773c0a",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Validating <b>HYPOTHESIS 1</b></span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Next, we examine a portion of the inventory belonging to their son, Pedro Dias:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgPD\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPD', '0%')\" class=\"imgGameSize\" src=\"images/Archive/PedroDias.png\" /><br /><b>Figure 2</b>: Excerpt from the inventory of Pedro Dias (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('3a98a6a5-5261-4d8a-b10b-05f7ff97b790'); return false;\">Invent\u00e1rios e Testamentos, <span class=\"htdate\"></span>, Volume 20, pp. 56 </a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "4c2e805a-a364-48c7-939c-b4dbfb5174e5",
         "prev": "09b4c8c7-be35-428a-ad4c-f4aee65aa354",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 0,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "top"
      },
      {
         "id": "4c2e805a-a364-48c7-939c-b4dbfb5174e5",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Validating <b>HYPOTHESIS 1</b></span><p>Although we do not know the name of Fern\u00e3o Dias Paes' father, we do know that his son, Pedro Dias (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('3a98a6a5-5261-4d8a-b10b-05f7ff97b790'); return false;\">Invent\u00e1rios e Testamentos, <span class=\"htdate\"></span>, Volume 14, pp. 314</a>), named his firstborn son Paschoal Leite after his father-in-law, Paschoal Leite (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('7bc10acc-8d54-41f3-b59d-deab9444f737'); return false;\">De Genere Jo\u00e3o Leite, <span class=\"htdate\"></span>, img. 49</a>). The second son, Fern\u00e3o Dias Paes, was named after his father (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('3a98a6a5-5261-4d8a-b10b-05f7ff97b790'); return false;\">Invent\u00e1rios e Testamentos, <span class=\"htdate\"></span>, Volume 20, pp. 56 </a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\">?</div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>But is this enough?</b><br />Can a single example validate a hypothesis and discard others?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": [
            "While a single example can support a hypothesis, it is risky to conclude an investigation based on a desired outcome, as this may reflect a very specific scenario. It is crucial to use the largest sample of available information to reinforce a hypothesis."
         ],
         "next": "07040d04-83a2-4bd4-9049-cde1955a2931",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 0,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "top"
      },
      {
         "id": "07040d04-83a2-4bd4-9049-cde1955a2931",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Continuing with <b>HYPOTHESIS 1</b></span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">When we analyze more details about the Leme family, we observe that Fern\u00e3o Dias Paes' firstborn grandson named his son Garcia Roiz, after his father-in-law (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('baab6f07-714e-40ca-abea-775fb55e1968'); return false;\">Torre do Tombo, Tribunal do Santo Of\u00edcio: Conselho Geral, Habilita\u00e7\u00f5es, Pedro, m\u00e7. 25, doc. 476, img. 159</a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><b>Another confirmation</b><br />Once again, it seems we have confirmation. However, can we truly discard other hypotheses?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": [
            "Although we are noticing a pattern, we are only studying generations within a single family. This does not allow us to generalize our conclusions. Now, let's examine another family from a different historical period. If the pattern persists, it might suggest that Fern\u00e3o Dias Paes, the grandfather, also had a grandfather with his name."
         ],
         "next": "",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 0,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "top"
      },
      {
         "id": "36dd9912-cbb3-4f4f-bad3-20721a48cdab",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Validating <b>HYPOTHESIS 2</b></span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Based on our current understanding of Banu Qasi genealogy, we hypothesize that Musa ibn Musa named his firstborn son Musa  (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('14fbd9a7-f358-4824-b16d-6ce5090b68f6'); return false;\">History Tracers, <span class=\"htdate\"></span></a>)...</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgMMF\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgMMF', '0%')\" class=\"imgGameSize\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/MusaMusaFortun.png\" /><br /><b>Figure 3</b>: Excerpt from the genealogical tree of Musa ibn Musa (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('14fbd9a7-f358-4824-b16d-6ce5090b68f6'); return false;\">History Tracers, <span class=\"htdate\"></span></a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "1da85556-60fc-4011-806b-b22b1c84a78a",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "top"
      },
      {
         "id": "1da85556-60fc-4011-806b-b22b1c84a78a",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Validating <b>HYPOTHESIS 2</b></span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">However, when we examine the Banu Qasi family, we find that this did not occur (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('b43eff03-c370-4692-875a-2455e2c99d03'); return false;\">Juste, Alberto C., <span class=\"htdate\"></span>, pp. 87</a>). Moreover, Musa ibn Musa should have been named Fortun ibn Musa, not Musa ibn Musa. These exceptions are also observed in other generations.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><b>Did We Discard a Hypothesis?</b><br />Does this research disprove <b>HYPOTHESIS 1</b>?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": [
            "Yes, the analysis of this family disproves <b>HYPOTHESIS 1</b>. This conclusion is drawn from the disruption observed in the patrilineal naming pattern. Additionally, due to the lack of information from the maternal lineage, we cannot make assertions about unmeasured aspects."
         ],
         "next": "a4d209af-4c5a-4e77-a8c4-1eab8b12f19b",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "top"
      },
      {
         "id": "a4d209af-4c5a-4e77-a8c4-1eab8b12f19b",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\"><b>HYPOTHESIS 3</b></span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HYPOTHESIS 1</b> was discarded after validating <b>HYPOTHESIS 2</b>. Since <b>HYPOTHESIS 3</b> cannot be true if any other hypothesis is valid, it is also discarded with the validation of <b>HYPOTHESIS 2</b>.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "42142c3a-a3fa-4cab-a29e-775adbe25d6b",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "42142c3a-a3fa-4cab-a29e-775adbe25d6b",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Tabulation</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">After conducting several experiments, the results were organized into a table to simplify comparison and theory formulation:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><table class=\"indigenous_period\"><tr><th>Experiments</th><th>HYPOTHESIS 1</th><th>HYPOTHESIS 2</th><th>HYPOTHESIS 3</th></tr> <tr><th>3 generations of the Leme</th><td><b>X</b></td><td><b>X</b></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>  <tr><th>Another generation of the Leme</th><td><b>X</b></td><td><b>X</b></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr> <tr><th>The Banu Qasi</th><td>&nbsp;</td><td><b>X</b></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr> </table>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "5b352012-0269-4e4e-a3b8-9647e3d3e361",
         "prev": "a4d209af-4c5a-4e77-a8c4-1eab8b12f19b",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "5b352012-0269-4e4e-a3b8-9647e3d3e361",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">The theory (1/2)</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">We began with three hypotheses:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HYPOTHESIS 1</b>: All firstborn sons receive the name of a grandfather.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HYPOTHESIS 2</b>: This occurs in some situations but is not a general rule.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HYPOTHESIS 3</b>: This never happens.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 2,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "559e6f37-1ff9-4409-8861-74afd56aa0be",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">The theory (2/2)</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">After conducting the experiments, we validated only <b>HYPOTHESIS 2</b>. Therefore, we propose the theory that firstborn sons receive a grandfather's name in certain scenarios (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('44acb900-ee84-4e42-8d9b-a947351af2cd'); return false;\">History Tracers (<span class=\"htdate\"></span>): Scientific Method</a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><center><i class=\"fa-solid fa-medal\" style=\"color:gold; font-size: 5vw\"></i></center></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      }
   ],
